{"tid":1824520,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家知唔知而家喺香港係買唔倒dji最新嘅model - Mavic Mini？點解？佢哋因為政治原因要懲罰香港人","createTime":"2020-01-14T13:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T16:28:14.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d3bc89c37e6ec95f2b1bfdeaec6d94e9d9f99711","tid":1824520,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知而家喺香港係買唔倒dji最新嘅model - Mavic Mini？點解？佢哋因為政治原因要懲罰香港人，行貨唔入口香港，官網網購都唔支援香港區。<br />\n之前有賣嘅Mavic 2系列而家都話「冇貨」。<br />\n無可否認，Dji係無人航拍機品牌嘅大哥大，全世界包括香港都有好多人係用家。但一個擺到明因政治理由唔賣嘢俾香港人嘅品牌，大家會唔會爭氣杯葛佢？<br />\n敢唔敢？捨唔捨得？自己諗吓。<br />\n(p.s.我之前曾經都喺呢度貼過有關呢個品牌嘅post，唔知點解冇出現過)"},{"pid":"35f8d46272b4d8f7fd6303a31f95a8d795c1da4c","tid":1824520,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/82283526_10157871162519395_1096109498281492480_o.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_ohc=HH9BgiGnDaAAX9P0fb0&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;_nc_tp=1&amp;oh=32faf379feaa820503958e79ad67f950&amp;oe=5E8EC4C3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F82283526_10157871162519395_1096109498281492480_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_ohc%3DHH9BgiGnDaAAX9P0fb0%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26_nc_tp%3D1%26oh%3D32faf379feaa820503958e79ad67f950%26oe%3D5E8EC4C3&h=bac8c609&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/2701324926545942/permalink/3019468064731625/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F2701324926545942%2Fpermalink%2F3019468064731625%2F&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerqCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=ed8c6c73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/2701324926545942/permalink/3019468064731625/</a>"},{"pid":"1e856088dab84cc73d6e8e65c78020b39d1a4e3a","tid":1824520,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:38:40.000Z","msg":"等緊mavic 3 出"},{"pid":"751ae939422d5fd65a0ab140c821b0c5b225f897","tid":1824520,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:39:17.000Z","msg":"dji仲有好多野可以買,唔單止係航拍機"},{"pid":"55d09ab0540d9e596ef9a2f8e1b9f0f69c76fe07","tid":1824520,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:41:43.000Z","msg":"並唔係比大陸收購，而係由頭到尾都係大陸，深圳公司，dji長寫係da jiang innovation"},{"pid":"47b93871ba2df1c072270f51338ac671ee445784","tid":1824520,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:42:14.000Z","msg":"大疆創新（英文：D&agrave;-Jiāng Innovations，簡稱DJI），全名為深圳大疆創新科技有限公司（英文：SZ D&agrave;-Jiāng Innovations Science and Technology Co., Ltd.），是中華人民共和國一家以生產、研發民用無人飛行載具及航空攝影系統為主的科技公司，企業總部位於廣東省深圳市，創始人汪滔。公司致力於為無人機工業、行業用戶以及專業航拍應用提供智能飛控產品和解決方案，通過持續的創新，大疆致力於為無人機工業、行業用戶以及專業航拍應用提供性能強、體驗佳的革命性智能飛控產品和解決方案。目前全球市場佔有率為70％[2]"},{"pid":"3e72f184452fcb969c27296cac0aaefb43718086","tid":1824520,"uid":130797,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:43:03.000Z","msg":"狗也不屌<br />\n入哂資料俾終國公司<br />\n寧願摺紙飛機玩算<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d56592be2b908b3af1d32daac5cde8a3911476","tid":1824520,"uid":3149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:45:32.000Z","msg":"咪仲好，唔駛俾機會佢賺外匯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27dedfe7d5c05686a5c07f7f2ebdb63a11999df","tid":1824520,"uid":39383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T14:00:52.000Z","msg":"唔賣仲好, 香港人咪比錢佢賺"},{"pid":"67d28431b0efd92e50479f0089b1219dd0e80bba","tid":1824520,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T14:01:40.000Z","msg":"佢開頭係扮外國公司，出左名先敢同人講係中企"},{"pid":"bae55a9f9e77d053ec93f2d7cf0494f7bf5bebb7","tid":1824520,"uid":321709,"li